# LC-MS Screening Assistant

Standalone LC-MS screening tool built with SvelteKit, Python, and PyTauri.

## Features
- LC-MS data screening and analysis.
- Modern Svelte 5 frontend.
- High-performance Rust/Python backend via PyTauri.
- Cross-platform support (Mac, Linux, Windows).

